import React from "react";

import { Form, Modal, Button, Header } from "semantic-ui-react";

import Context from "./"

export default function AddProductForm() {
  return (
    <Modal trigger={<Button primary>Add new Product</Button>}>
      <Modal.Header>Add new Product</Modal.Header>
      <Modal.Content>
        <Form>
          <Form.Input label="Name" placeholder="Product name" />
          <Form.Input
            label="Description"
            placeholder="Product description (Optional)"
          />
          <Form.Group widths="equal">
            <Form.Input label="Price" placeholder="Price (USD)" />
            <Form.Input label="Weight" placeholder="Weigth (Kg)" />
          </Form.Group>
          <Form.Group widths="equal">
            <Form.Input label="Image 1" placeholder="Image 1 URL" />
            <Form.Input label="Image 2" placeholder="Image 2 URL" />
            <Form.Input label="Image 3" placeholder="Image 3 URL" />
          </Form.Group>
          <Button type="submit">Add</Button>
        </Form>
      </Modal.Content>
    </Modal>
  );
}
